import React from 'react'
import { Card } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Container = () => (
  <Card.Group itemsPerRow={4}>
    <Card.Content textAlign="center" />
        <Card.Content
          style={{
            height: "300px",
            width:"300px",
            backgroundImage: 'url(/map.png)',
            backgroundSize: "cover",
            margin:"20px",
            overlay: {
              opacity: 0.5,
              backgroundColor: 'black'
            },
          }}
        >
          <Card.Description style={{ color: "white" }}>
            Hello World!
          </Card.Description>
        </Card.Content>

        <Card.Content textAlign="center" />
        <Card.Content
          style={{
            height: "300px",
            width:"300px",
            backgroundImage: 'url(/friends.jpg)',
            backgroundSize: "cover",
            margin:"20px"
          }}
        >
          <Card.Description style={{ color: "white" }}>
            Hello World!
          </Card.Description>
        </Card.Content>

        <Card.Content textAlign="center" />
        <Card.Content
          style={{
            height: "300px",
            width:"300px",
            backgroundImage: 'url(/restaurant.jpg)',
            backgroundSize: "cover",
            margin:"20px"
          }}
        >
          <Card.Description style={{ color: "white" }}>
            Hello World!
          </Card.Description>
        </Card.Content>
  </Card.Group>
)

export default Container
